This paper deals with capacity and optimal signaling schemes for a MISO channel, which is a topic in information theory and communication systems (cs.IT and cs.COMM). The paper also considers the cases of constant channel and Rayleigh fading channel, which are topics in signal processing and wireless communication (cs.SI and cs.NI). Finally, the paper discusses the impact of power constraints on capacity, which is a topic in control systems and optimization (cs.SY).
